<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="smart-adj">smart <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /smɑːt/    美 /smɑːrt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>聪明的；精明的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary’s teacher says she’s one of the smartest kids in the class. 
玛丽的老师说她是班上最聪明的孩子之一。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You are quite smart about business.
你做生意很精明。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>漂亮的；潇洒的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>look smart</strong> in this red jacket.
你穿这件红色夹克真漂亮。</p><footer>2008 湖北</footer></div></div>